	<Title>
		Narrow stools: Should I be concerned?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Narrow stools may be a sign of narrowing or obstruction of the colon.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		What causes narrow stools? Should I be concerned?
	</Question>
